Description.note: A woman takes Communion during a Plaza Church mass for the fiesta of Nuestra Senora de Guadalupe.|~|Our Lady Queen of Los Angeles Catholic Church, (aka La Iglesia de Nuestra Señora la Reina de Los Ángeles, and The Church of Our Lady the Queen of the Angels), was built in 1822 and is the oldest church in Los Angeles.
